Package: dagml
Title: R Binding for DAG-ML Local Implementations
Version: 0.2.7
Authors@R: person("Gregory", "Beurier", email = "gregory.beurier@cirad.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Retains R loss and metric functions in process-local registries
    keyed by validated DAG-ML implementation descriptors. Training controllers
    can execute local functions during FIT_CV and REFIT and return native
    DAG-ML loss attestations without serializing executable code.
License: CeCILL-2.1 | AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/GBeurier/dag-ml
BugReports: https://github.com/GBeurier/dag-ml/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Suggests: jsonlite
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: no
